cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL

The paper deals with the analysis of geospatial streams and the prediction of future locations based on user behavior. This falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of graph algorithms and neural networks also suggests a focus on data mining (cs.SD) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
